    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Machines that knead and/or form dough or pastry into sheets of consistent thickness between horizontal steel rollers. These devices have been made in two forms: simple and return; the second is able to reverse the motion. The distance between rollers is reduced to bring the dough to a desired thickness.</Note_Text>
